  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a 38-week, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel group trial of
      approximately 150 patients who have a history of immediate hypersensitivity reaction to
      peanut protein.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
